{"tid":2010603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英指點黃色經濟圈, 可從原材料去中國化","createTime":"2020-05-10T13:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T17:06:20.000Z","uid":185628,"like":33,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"308940e2fcc9db12fd53f4f964633f99a44e6881","tid":2010603,"uid":185628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T13:48:10.000Z","msg":"同樣地，什麼才算黃店，也沒有人可以說清楚。不必拒絕用大陸食材，不必拒絕僱用(親共的)新移民，總之你說黃就是黃。這種「入線」極為容易，表面上沒有什麼成本，但對生意有幫助嗎？只要看看出名黃的冰室，執完一間又一間。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英其實暗中提點民主派, 一個企業鏈包括品牌,平台,材料,加工,運輸,員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n品牌,加工:<br />\n支持香港親民主品牌+加工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料: <br />\n以盡量不影響成本為前提, 罷用中國材料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(東江水可以唔抵制，因為港共政府每年都會俾同樣嘅錢，已經係固定支出)<br />\n<br />\n平台:<br />\n已經有各大黃店apps<br />\n可以諗多d辦法提醒埋香港人邊間係藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如用交友apps提醒附近嘅人邊間係藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n運輸:<br />\n整黃色food panda+順豐<br />\n<br />\n員工:<br />\n盡量請返 黃員工<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100010574583275/posts/1157667144595761/?sfnsn=mo[/url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100010574583275%2Fposts%2F1157667144595761%2F%3Fsfnsn%3Dmo%5B%2Furl&d=18ndJK2uCT0lbSM6MbdNQr3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=9cb86871\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100010574583275/posts/1157667144595761/?sfnsn=mo[/url</a>"},{"pid":"7b0d0fa9a5ca5bb10179fc49cabc6e289d34bf80","tid":2010603,"uid":185628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T13:48:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100010574583275/posts/1157667144595761/?sfnsn=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100010574583275%2Fposts%2F1157667144595761%2F%3Fsfnsn%3Dmo&d=18ndJK2uCT0lbSM6MbdNQr3